<p><span style="font-size:80%;"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/sarkicism-hub">Sarkicism Hub</a><br />
<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/an-anthropological-approach-to-sarkicism-case-study-02-the-d">&lt;&lt; Case Study 02: The Divoši of Prague</a> | <strong>Case Study 03: The Darkwater Lodge</strong> |</span></p>
